{"tid":1569296,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"P牌仔想講少少野 希望大家入黎睇一睇","createTime":"2019-09-14T14:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T14:34:16.000Z","uid":310572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"20d88877ed09f34b0e78ca02e0abc46c6b7d157a","tid":1569296,"uid":310572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">第一 國際戰線</span></span><br />\n本地文宣其實算夠 但係國際戰線真係嚴重不足 雖然好多外國人都知香港發生咩事 但係唔知係咁大件事 我地有大把彈藥 煲大佢！同埋要煲大對家同我地嘅分別 邊個先係暴徒 邊個唔理智 我覺得呢幾個國家要落足火藥：<br />\n1. 美國<br />\n2. 英國<br />\n3. 台灣<br />\n4. 德國<br />\n5. 澳洲（其實呢個國家少文宣 但係佢地係第一個國家ban華為 同埋成個國家都比支那人入侵 本地人多多少少都會唔滿意 所以都應該connect埋佢地）<br />\n6. 印度（呢個應該唔洗多講 咖喱國啲人口拍得住支國 網絡戰有得打）<br />\n其實我覺得中國都可以connect下 始終咁多人 有0.1%都已經好多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">第二 重建連儂牆</span></span><br />\n其實連儂牆真係一個低風險又高回報嘅活動 唔明點解越黎越少人做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第三 搞狗屋</span></span><br />\n老豆搵仔都已經起哂啲黑警底咁滯 點解唔搞搞佢 起碼令佢地番工放工都仲要提心吊膽 仲要驚屋企人受傷等等 令佢地心理有壓力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第四 算好的不分化不割蓆呢</span></span><br />\n其實我地要不分化 不割蓆<br />\n而家日日有人屌唱歌 又屌first aid救人 但係點解唔唸一個兩全其美嘅辦法solve佢<br />\n例如 唱歌可以合併連儂牆<br />\nFirst-aid救對家 又冇阻你再打多次 咪救完打 救完打<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">第五 唔好有失敗主義</span></span><br />\n呢個真係好重要 因為negative嘅野好快會傳播同受感染 而家個個都鼓吹個運動似雨革 美國德國英國唔幫我地等等 咁又點？無論人地幫唔幫都要靠自己努力 唔爭取到最後一刻都唔叫輸！<br />\n人地幫你只係一個bonus<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">第六 對家做超級進化 我地要做究極進化</span></span><br />\n對家點進化唔洗講 我地就比佢進化得勁啲 <br />\n例如 滲入撐警集會遊行 揸住枝國旗為所欲為 對家又會開始分化 開始篤灰 好過直接做佢對立面同佢對抗<br />\n我只想如果人地準備50% 你咪準備到100% 人地凖備100% 你就準備到150%<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">第七 罷食罷買</span></span><br />\n呢點勇武和理非左膠都一定做到 而黃藍商店圖如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BNJZ8rT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBNJZ8rT.jpg&h=865a140d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9xj8rU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9xj8rU.jpg&h=ec0ad0cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BNRH6dA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBNRH6dA.jpg&h=8f9cc602&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vj7PMdC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVj7PMdC.jpg&h=6b0d1392&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OWTZ8rY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOWTZ8rY.jpg&h=7c1ee357&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yn7L30m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyn7L30m.jpg&h=bf6a3613&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H7d3QFo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH7d3QFo.jpg&h=351de9ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6cMMOr6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6cMMOr6.jpg&h=f4c50238&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qz1kSTO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQz1kSTO.jpg&h=1e4812f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7dKbe7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7dKbe7a.jpg&h=7d791469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後 聽日見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9715eb211f555ce013f7352cf23a345a20dfc1c0","tid":1569296,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg